Package: libargus-gsi-pep-callout1
Architecture: any
Depends: libargus-pep2, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Argus PEP client callout module for Globus GSI (gridftp).
 This GSI module does callout to the Argus Authorization Service to authorize 
 the user based on its credentials and returns a user mapping.
